headline.main: Bahrain Files Lawsuit to Dissolve Secular Political Party
headline.print_headline: Bahrain Files Lawsuit to Dissolve Secular Political Party

lead_paragraph: Bahrain's government filed a lawsuit Monday to dissolve a secular political party, the second-such organization it has targeted in the last year as part of an intense crackdown on opposition in the island nation.
